Again, you didn't pay attention to (or simply can't understand) the distinction between avoidance and mitigation AC. Monks pre ROK had about the same mitigation AC as druids, often less. 200 mitigation AC on a monk was pretty damn good back then. The raw AC available from items for monks back then simply didn't allow monks to get much mitigation AC without losing a large part of their avoidance AC benefit.<br>
<br>
